{"tid":1905334,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"強國3月新政策：不會再有李文亮醫生了","createTime":"2020-03-01T07:46:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T18:10:31.000Z","uid":222513,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fdf390f0f462855e0ce1c1c84b42b441702526b3","tid":1905334,"uid":222513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T07:46:54.000Z","msg":"[把牆推倒] 支那網民要求取消網絡長城<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1905173/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1905173/page/1</a><br />\n呢個po已經講咗中國今日有更嚴厲打壓網上言論自由嘅政策 (前排班強國人仲覺得係微博悼念李文亮醫生好撚有言論自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 同日就有班追星小粉紅舉報到一個ff文網站係強國被牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nIf TLDR: 係連登討論完上twitter retweet 唔該<br />\n<br />\n1. THREAD: Sad day for Chinese internet users: Ao3, archive of our own, was reportedly blocked <a href=\"https://twitter.com/muge_niu/status/1233762832556154880?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmuge_niu%2Fstatus%2F1233762832556154880%3Fs%3D21&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGojMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=509a8890\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmuge_niu%2Fstatus%2F1233762832556154880%3Fs%3D21&h=59d64823\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/muge_niu/status/1233762832556154880?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 仲提返起六四<a href=\"https://twitter.com/muge_niu/status/1233762865041092608?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmuge_niu%2Fstatus%2F1233762865041092608%3Fs%3D21&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGojMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=17e10d21\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmuge_niu%2Fstatus%2F1233762865041092608%3Fs%3D21&h=5544897d\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/muge_niu/status/1233762865041092608?s=21</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v1p3nDf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv1p3nDf.jpg&h=52ea1b9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. Ao3官方 tweet<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ao3_status/status/1233892047804911619?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fao3_status%2Fstatus%2F1233892047804911619%3Fs%3D21&d=Nx8B%2FL5SKgEDk9M5z9cGojMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=9f15efd5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fao3_status%2Fstatus%2F1233892047804911619%3Fs%3D21&h=0417f395\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ao3_status/status/1233892047804911619?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"06ca236d17386ae6822774c5d7d50e9cabf20377","tid":1905334,"uid":222513,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T07:49:49.000Z","msg":"件事係咪咁簡單？常見中共手段：民鬥民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家成班強國人狗衝去屌啲追星小粉紅 但其實係共產黨封嘅網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nAo3唔係普通嘅論壇 寫ff文寫到舊年攞 Hugo Award for Best Related Work (雨果獎) 而女性係雨果獎亦都越黎越受到重視 <br />\nff文就見得多 但今次班追星小粉紅係因BL+黃文先舉報個網站 當各位老婆gakki嘅掟上今日子已經講BL, 50 shades都已經上映完幾年 <br />\n中國仲係河蟹很黃很暴力 肺炎嘅中國高中online courses 上bio堂講講下性器官被和諧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實中國嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">言論自由 同性別權利嘅自由</span>根本就每況越下 <br />\n<br />\n難得中共助攻記得上twitter retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好唔記得我地爭取嘅人權 五大訴求 <br />\n同琴日嘅831</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再講句上連登po膠文嘅公關po仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e21d6cd86cf71d48a484fc5adfec9a7c5d054c","tid":1905334,"uid":222513,"like":0,"dislike":0